data.description: You do not want to miss this charming 3 bed/2 bath with an open floor plan and a SPACIOUS backyard. Living room flooring was updated to a lovely, neutral laminate and a new water heater was installed March 2023. The laundry room & kitchen are spacious and functional and come with plenty of storage. Second bath features a tub & shower. Primary bath features a shower, only. Home also comes with fridge, washer and dryer. It is move-in ready and the perfect starter home. Located in the well-kept, gated community of Colonia Del Norte, residence have access to a beautiful community pool and park as well as RV storage. Convenient access to I-17 and the 101, and located near Acacia Elementary which is an Arizona ''A'' Rated school AND an Arizona A++++ School of Excellen
